(6, 1, 'announcement', 'openrouter', 'arcee-ai/trinity-mini:free', 'arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free', 'arcee-ai/trinity-mini:free', '{\"feature\":\"announcement\",\"input\":{\"topic\":\"Pengambilan barcode BPNT\",\"brief\":\"Pengambilan barcode BPNT di rumah kepala dusun masing-masing dengan membawa KTP sebagai syarat pengambilan.\",\"tone\":\"informatif\",\"length\":\"medium\",\"keywords\":\"Barcode BPNT\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"system\",\"content\":\"Anda adalah penyusun pengumuman resmi Desa Lambanggelun.\\nTulisan harus lugas, ringkas, dan memberi pengumuman informasi yang jelas untuk warga.\\nBalasan wajib satu objek JSON valid saja tanpa markdown atau teks tambahan.\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Topik utama: Pengambilan barcode BPNT\\nInformasi\\/deskripsi operator: Pengambilan barcode BPNT di rumah kepala dusun masing-masing dengan membawa KTP sebagai syarat pengambilan.\\nGaya penulisan: informatif\\nPanjang konten: sedang (4-5 paragraf)\\nKata kunci penting: Barcode BPNT\\nHasilkan JSON dengan struktur:\\n{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"string, maksimal 120 karakter\\\",\\n  \\\"content\\\": \\\"string, isi pengumuman resmi dengan poin waktu\\/tempat\\/syarat bila tersedia dengan panjang 200 kata\\\"\\n}\"}]}', '{\"raw\":{\"id\":\"gen-1771589580-694rGr9YofzoAOMPXuaq\",\"provider\":\"Arcee AI\",\"model\":\"arcee-ai\\/trinity-mini:free\",\"object\":\"chat.completion\",\"created\":1771589581,\"choices\":[{\"logprobs\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"native_finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"index\":0,\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"\\n\\n{\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"Pengambilan Barcode BPNT di Rumah Kepala Dusun\\\",\\n  \\\"content\\\": \\\"Desa Lambanggelun menyampaikan informasi resmi tentang pengambilan Barcode BPNT. Warga desa yang membutuhkan Barcode BPNT diwajibkan untuk mengambilnya di rumah kepala dusun masing-masing. Pengambilan dilakukan dengan membawa KTP sebagai bukti identitas. Proses ini dilaksanakan secara rutin sesuai jadwal yang telah ditetapkan. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut atau jadwal spesifik, warga dapat menghubungi kepala dusun di desa ini. Perhatikan untuk membawa KTP saat mengambil Barcode BPNT untuk proses pendaftaran yang lancar.\\\"\\n}\",\"refusal\":null,\"reasoning\":\"Okay, let me start by understanding the user\'s request. They want a JSON structure for a formal village announcement about taking BPNT barcodes. The key points are that the barcode pickup is at each village head\'s house, requiring a KTP. The tone should be informative, and the content should be 4-5 paragraphs long, around 200 words.\\n\\nFirst, I need to ensure the JSON structure has the title and content fields. The title must be under 120 characters. The content should include all necessary details: time, place, requirements, and any other relevant info. Since the user mentioned it\'s a formal announcement, the language should be clear and concise.\\n\\nWait, the user specified that the response must be a single JSON object without any markdown or extra text. So I can\'t add anything beyond the JSON. Also, the content must be a string, so I need to format it properly. Let me check the keywords: BPNT, KTP, village head\'s house. Make sure those are included.\\n\\nI should structure the content with paragraphs covering the purpose, location, requirements, and any additional instructions. Let me count the words to ensure it\'s around 200. Also, avoid markdown, so just plain text with line breaks represented by \\\\n. \\n\\nDouble-check the title length. \\\"Pengambilan Barcode BPNT di Rumah Kepala Dusun\\\" is 50 characters, which is under 120. Good. Now, the content should flow naturally, informing residents about the process, where to go, what documents to bring, and maybe the schedule. Since the user didn\'t specify a date, I\'ll keep it general. \\n\\nMake sure all required info is included: each dusun\'s head house, KTP as a requirement. Avoid any markdown, just plain text. Alright, that should cover it. Let me put it all together in the correct JSON format.\\n\",\"reasoning_details\":[{\"format\":\"unknown\",\"index\":0,\"type\":\"reasoning.text\",\"text\":\"Okay, let me start by understanding the user\'s request. They want a JSON structure for a formal village announcement about taking BPNT barcodes. The key points are that the barcode pickup is at each village head\'s house, requiring a KTP. The tone should be informative, and the content should be 4-5 paragraphs long, around 200 words.\\n\\nFirst, I need to ensure the JSON structure has the title and content fields. The title must be under 120 characters. The content should include all necessary details: time, place, requirements, and any other relevant info. Since the user mentioned it\'s a formal announcement, the language should be clear and concise.\\n\\nWait, the user specified that the response must be a single JSON object without any markdown or extra text. So I can\'t add anything beyond the JSON. Also, the content must be a string, so I need to format it properly. Let me check the keywords: BPNT, KTP, village head\'s house. Make sure those are included.\\n\\nI should structure the content with paragraphs covering the purpose, location, requirements, and any additional instructions. Let me count the words to ensure it\'s around 200. Also, avoid markdown, so just plain text with line breaks represented by \\\\n. \\n\\nDouble-check the title length. \\\"Pengambilan Barcode BPNT di Rumah Kepala Dusun\\\" is 50 characters, which is under 120. Good. Now, the content should flow naturally, informing residents about the process, where to go, what documents to bring, and maybe the schedule. Since the user didn\'t specify a date, I\'ll keep it general. \\n\\nMake sure all required info is included: each dusun\'s head house, KTP as a requirement. Avoid any markdown, just plain text. Alright, that should cover it. Let me put it all together in the correct JSON format.\\n\"}]}}],\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"usage\":