gelun. They need a JSON structure with specific elements. The main topic is the Pendaftaran Lomba Krenova, which is a district-level competition open to the public and students. The operator\'s info mentions it\'s linked, and the style should be informative. The content needs to be concise, around 2-3 paragraphs, with keywords like creativity and innovation.\\n\\nFirst, I need to ensure the JSON structure is correct. The title must be under 120 characters. The content should include time, place, and conditions if available. Since the user mentioned the link is already attached, I don\'t need to include it here. \\n\\nI\'ll start by crafting a title that\'s catchy and includes the main keywords. Maybe \\\"Pendaftaran Lomba Krenova Tingkat Kabupaten Pekalongan\\\" to highlight the event\'s name and level. Then, the content should mention the competition\'s purpose, open participation, and the link. I need to keep it under 200 words. \\n\\nWait, the user specified the content should be a string with 200 words maximum. Let me check the word count. The draft content is around 100 words, which is fine. I should include the keywords \\\"kreatifitas inovasi\\\" in the content. Also, ensure the JSON is valid without any markdown or extra text. \\n\\nDouble-checking the structure: title and content are the only keys. No markdown, just plain JSON. Make sure the JSON syntax is correct, with proper quotes and commas. Alright, that should cover all the requirements.\\n\"}]}}],\"system_fingerprint\":null,\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":226,\"completion_tokens\":531,\"total_tokens\":757,\"cost\":0,\"is_byok\":false,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"cost_details\":{\"upstream_inference_cost\":0,\"upstream_inference_prompt_cost\":0,\"upstream_inference_completions_cost\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":390,\"audio_tokens\":0}}},\"parsed\":{\"title\":\"Pendaftaran Lomba Krenova Kabupaten Pekalongan\",\"content\":\"Desa Lambanggelun mengumumkan pendaftaran Lomba Krenova Tingkat Kabupaten Pekalongan. Lomba ini terbuka untuk semua warga dan pelajar. Fokusnya pada kreativitas dan inovasi. Informasi lengkap dan link pendaftaran sudah disampaikan melalui saluran resmi desa. Peserta diharapkan mempersiapkan karya yang mencerminkan kemampuan kreatifitas dalam bidang krenova. Tim pemenang akan diumumkan pada tanggal tertentu setelah penilaian. Silakan kunjungi laman resmi Desa Lambanggelun untuk melakukan pendaftaran segera.\"}}', 'success', NULL, '2026-02-20 09:28:59', '2026-02-20 09:28:59');
